flowchart LR
    subgraph "SMS Sending Flow"
        A[User in Call] --> B{Select Action}
        B -->|Template| C[Choose Template]
        B -->|Custom| D[Compose Message]
        C --> E[Preview Message]
        D --> E
        E --> F[Variable Replacement]
        F --> G[Send via Telnyx]
        G --> H{Success?}
        H -->|Yes| I[Update UI<br/>Show Status]
        H -->|No| J[Queue for Retry]
        J --> G
        I --> K[Store in History]
        J --> L[Show Error]
    end


